\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.7}{\ignorespaces Transient companion model: a capacitor is replaced by a conductance $\alpha C$ in parallel with a current source, enabling purely algebraic MNA solution at each timestep.}}{64}{figure.6.7}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.8}{\ignorespaces Adaptive timestep behaviour during a transient simulation: timestep shrinks during rapid transitions and grows during quiescent periods.}}{65}{figure.6.8}%
